Memang payah.

381
00:24:32,282 --> 00:24:34,841
Aku baru saja melakukan operasi
hernia bersama Dr. Bell.

382
00:24:34,851 --> 00:24:36,447
Dia memiliki tangan ajaib.

383
00:24:40,539 --> 00:24:42,659
<i>Dr. Flores, hubungi 182--</i>

384
00:24:42,669 --> 00:24:43,728
Hei.

385
00:24:43,738 --> 00:24:46,229
Randolph, senang kau disini.

386
00:24:47,227 --> 00:24:49,311
Dimana lagi aku harus berada?

387
00:24:50,007 --> 00:24:51,904
Sebaiknya kau menghabiskan
salad tiram itu.

388
00:24:51,905 --> 00:24:53,370
Tak boleh makan setelah
tengah malam.

389
00:24:53,380 --> 00:24:55,071
Baiklah. Rasanya sangat lezat.

390
00:24:55,072 --> 00:24:57,611
Lantai VIP ini luar biasa.

391
00:24:57,621 --> 00:24:59,529
Kau pantas mendapatkannya, sobat.

392
00:25:00,883 --> 00:25:02,863
Jika bukan karena donasi darimu,...

393
00:25:02,864 --> 00:25:05,701
